        <div class="hs-popup" id="hs-resp-2">
          <button class="pop-close" onclick="closePopup('hs-resp-2')">✕</button>
          <div class="pop-label"><span class="pop-accent" style="background:var(--resp)"></span>Primary Inspiratory Muscle</div>
          <h4>Diaphragm</h4>
          <p>The dome-shaped primary muscle of inspiration, innervated by the <strong>phrenic nerve (C3–C5)</strong>. When it contracts and flattens, the thoracic cavity lengthens vertically, creating negative intrapulmonary pressure that draws air in. For speech, the diaphragm relaxes gradually during exhalation as the abdominal muscles take over pressure regulation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hs-popup" id="hs-resp-3">
